# Formspree: Two forms (recommended for client work)
#
# 1. TESTING: Create a form at https://formspree.io with YOUR email.
#    Use this for development. Copy your form endpoint below.
#
# 2. PRODUCTION: At launch, create a second form with the CLIENT's email.
#    Set VITE_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT in your hosting provider (Netlify, Vercel, etc.).
#
# For local dev, copy this file to .env and add your test form endpoint:
VITE_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_TEST_FORM_ID
